2. cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper applies the proposed algorithm to the problem of face recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a new algorithm for clustering, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper may be relevant to this subcategory if the clustering algorithm is applied to natural language processing tasks. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper may be relevant to this subcategory if the clustering algorithm is implemented using neural networks or evolutionary algorithms.
